      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Trello MCP v2\n\n**18 tools across 4 domains**\n\n**Boards:** get_all_boards, get_board_members, get_board_labels\n**Lists:** get_lists_on_board, get_list_cards, create_list, archive_list\n**Cards:** get_board_cards, get_card_details, search_cards, create_card, update_card, archive_card, move_card, assign_member, assign_label\n**Comments:** get_comments, add_comment\n\n⚠️ Assign your Trello API credential to all nodes after import.",
